  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63685157.pdf_105_3",
    "text": "第一季《中国好声音》学员，摇滚唱作人， 搜狐公众号作者。 已发行个人专辑《NEWDAY》。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09638368235552684,
      0.611056414131267,
      0.39131775036343897,
      0.6643700610017802
    ],
